                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl scroll-reveal fade-in-up stagger-1">
                    Share your story with the <span class="text-rotate">
                        <span class="word">world.</span>
                        <span class="word">audience.</span>
                        <span class="word">readers.</span>
                        <span class="word">community.</span>
                    </span>
