                </p>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6 scroll-reveal fade-in-up stagger-3">
                    <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="rounded-md bg-teal-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-teal-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-teal-600 transition-all hover:scale-105">Get started</a>
