                    Focus on writing. We prioritize the reading experience and provide you with the tools to manage your content effortlessly.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
                <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
                    <div class="relative pl-16 scroll-reveal fade-in-right stagger-1">
                        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600">
                                <i data-lucide="pen-tool" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                            </div>
                            Clean Editor
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Distraction-free environment tailored for writers. Markdown support, auto-save, and rich formatting.</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16 scroll-reveal fade-in-left stagger-2">
                        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600">
                                <i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                            </div>
                            Analytics
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Understand your audience with detailed insights on views, reading time, and engagement.</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16 scroll-reveal fade-in-right stagger-3">
                        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600">
                                <i data-lucide="zap" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                            </div>
                            Fast Performance
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Built on Symfony and Tailwind for blazing fast load times and SEO optimization right out of the box.</dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16 scroll-reveal fade-in-left stagger-4">
                        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600">
                                <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                            </div>
                            Secure
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Enterprise-grade security with role-based access control to keep your content and data safe.</dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# How It Works Section #}
    <div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
