                            <div class="flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-500 text-white text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">1</div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Create Account</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Sign up for free and set up your author profile in under a minute.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative text-center scroll-reveal fade-in-up stagger-2">
